### <%= @class_header %> : set_special_description()
``` lua
meta:set_special_description( "I'm a custom creation!" )
```

This function assigns the *text* that will be shown when selecting this <% @meta_class %>.

#### Function Call
`meta:set_special_description( desc )`

#### Parameters
**`string`** `desc`<br>
&emsp;_The *text blurb* that will show up while selecting this <b><code><%= @meta_class %></code></b>._
